Intro:

In this episode, we dive deep into the world of day game, specifically focusing on what to expect when meeting women during the day.

St. Robert is an expert in day game and has valuable insights and advice to share. We explore the four different ways to meet women – social circle, night bars/clubs, online dating, and of course, day game. We discuss the pros and cons of each approach, highlighting why day game can be a game-changer for those looking to build their confidence and meet women in a more authentic way.

Looks play a significant role in attracting women, and St. Robert breaks down how being average-looking can be sufficient, while being model-looking can provide an added advantage. However, we also discuss how in more traditional environments, looks may play a lesser role, and social skills become paramount.

Throughout the episode, St. Robert shares personal anecdotes and insights from his coaching experiences to help listeners understand the journey of learning day game. We address common questions about day game for different types of people, the challenges faced by introverts and extroverts, and the role of age in finding success in dating.

We also delve into the importance of having a structured system in day gaming, understanding the power of storytelling and teasing, and knowing what to say to engage women from the very first minute.

But it's not just about approaching women – we also touch on the psychology of rejection and the specific challenges faced by black and brown men. We explore the impact of approach anxiety and how to overcome it, as well as the importance of adapting style and grooming to meet local standards.

So, join us on this episode as we unravel the world of day game and provide you with the tools and insights you need to boost your inner confidence and find success in dating. And don't forget to check out the free video St. Robert offers, explaining why most people struggle and how to find success in day gaming.
